  "description": [
    "MEET 00 THE FIRST ISSUE OF THE NEW ENLARGED NORTH WEST WORKERS PAPER _ Today the Voice of Action as r the appearance of a grown UP newspaper Bigger bettert be nu an even greater weapon in the hands of the workers and farm ers of the Pacific Northwest This growth of our press is a great achievement for us all those who work on the paper every agent very supporter every reader We can affford to be proud But we cannot afford to rest on our laurels We must at once plan how to get this more effective paper into more homes We must add hundreds of subsecribers to the list New subscription blanks will be off the press soon with the new Tates 200 a year SIOO for six manths and for the duration of the three months subscription drive to start right away 60 cents for three months Order them but dont wait for them ta arrive Sign your neigh bors your shop mates up now and send in their names Further details of the sub drive will be printed soon Special features appear today We want your opinion of them There are the Womens World the"
